cp .build/release/MyMCPServer /usr/local/bin/
```

## Integration with Claude Desktop

Add to `claude_desktop_config.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "my-mcp-server": {
      "command": "/path/to/MyMCPServer"
    }
  }
}
```
